name: Leo'sCarbohydrateFactList
0:
”Alexa, ask leo's carb list to tell me a fact”
”Alexa, open leo's carb list”
”Alexa, tell leo's carb list to give me a carb fact”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: leo's carb list
des: Contains lists of foods, serving size, and how many grams are in those servings. Also has a few general tips such as which food types are high-carb vs. low carb. Having to start watching carbs can be a bit dreary for some, so there's a bit of snarky humor here and there.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
